sentences: Aoi Tada (多田葵, Tada Aoi, born 3 July 1981 in Tokyo) is a Japanese singer and former voice actress.
In March 2005, she signed on to Moon-Bunny Entertainment and began her singer-songwriting career.
As of 2005, she has retired from voice acting but is still active as a singer.
